description: Maximize your workouts with the CAP Power Cage with High-Low Pulleys. Featuring six safety catch height adjustments, four solid cold rolled steel catches, upper and lower lat/low row pulley system, two plate storage posts, and 12- and 14-gauge steel tubing, this power cage is the ultimate piece of strength equipment. The recommended maximum weight capacity of this power cage is 1450 lbs, that’s more than half a ton! The recommended weight capacity for the bar catches is 500 lbs. The lat pull and low row attachments recommended weight capacity is 300 lbs, and the plate posts can hold standard or Olympic plates up to 325 lbs. This rack is finished in a durable powder coat finish and comes with industrial zinc hardware to provide exceptional maintenance-free durability.
